{"tid":1968572,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"無愛嘅拍拖係咪拍拖","createTime":"2020-04-11T18:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T02:34:04.000Z","uid":228436,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2962cc2f0d48511deb85fbf129eb08eed4f47aec","tid":1968572,"uid":228436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:16:11.000Z","msg":"係交友app識咗個女仔<br />\n傾咗就快四個月 都幾啱傾<br />\n個樣都正正常常咁 我覺得幾順眼<br />\n約過出黎幾次 相處都幾舒服<br />\n<br />\n佢啱啱同我講話其實鍾意咗我一段時間<br />\n話想同我一齊發展<br />\n<br />\n我其實係想拍拖<br />\n而且覺得好似同呢個女仔拍拖都無咩所謂咁<br />\n但係其實自問自己對佢其實無咩feel<br />\n我其實對佢無「愛情」<br />\n純粹因為唔反感所以就應承咗<br />\n<br />\n依家過咗個一刻<br />\n諗返轉頭好似唔多對路<br />\n<br />\n各位Ching有咩睇法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n指點下迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a224086760bc096e440faff4b1048470d165a37c","tid":1968572,"uid":74278,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:17:31.000Z","msg":"唔係咩叫拍散拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5009bcfef7e7738970829da5073e174bf17be59a","tid":1968572,"uid":78141,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:19:14.000Z","msg":"愛情係好玩但唔好玩愛情"},{"pid":"62b7b95f5a6940b11aa60f395936df168b7aa01c","tid":1968572,"uid":312142,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:19:33.000Z","msg":"唔好害人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa3f68b5867f86e43b33e20115bb4352a2479c8","tid":1968572,"uid":27416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:20:43.000Z","msg":"唔肚餓都可以食野架啫"},{"pid":"99ceee095fa696951d0cbf2cfa16453fe09d488d","tid":1968572,"uid":40979,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T18:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"